==Dutch==

===Verb===
'''afspreken'''
# To [[agree]].
#: ''Afgesproken!'' &mdash; Deal!.
# To make an appointment.
#: ''Laten we morgen afspreken.'' &mdash; Let's make an appointment for tomorrow / let's make an appointment tomorrow.

